727258f-a.title: Queens: Little Neck Parkway - 40th Avenue
727258f-a.text:
Little Neck Parkway, west side, at 40th Avenue, showing
an old house, having been the property of Morgan in 1873 and
1891. It is opposite the Little Neck Railroad station. The
Parkway is the former Old House Landing Road.
P. L. Sperr  June 10, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
